Cell["\<\
By default no idempotent representation is used, since the tower is simple.  \
Idempotent representation can be enforced by using the option \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]UseAlwaysIdempotents\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]->True. \
The output has to be equal, since the remainder is 0 for any Complete \
Reduction.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.990172408134012*^9, 3.990172541261285*^9}, {
  3.9901725935251303`*^9, 
